      - JG546AAE  HP IMC Basic SW Platform w/50-node E-LTU
      - JG548AAE  HP PCM+ to IMC Bsc Upgr w/50-node E-LTU
      - JG549AAE  HP PCM+ to IMC Std Upgr w/200-node E-LTU
